        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Intervalle"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Intervals are the distance between two notes. Choose which intervals you want to practice. Start with a few and add more as you gain confidence." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Intervalle sind der Abstand zwischen zwei Tönen. Wähle aus, welche Intervalle du üben möchtest. Beginne mit wenigen und füge weitere hinzu, wenn du sicherer wirst."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Just Intonation" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Reine Stimmung"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Just pick any training mode on the home screen and start practicing. Peach adapts to your skill level automatically." : {
      "localizations" : {
